    <item>
      <title>特朗普建议万斯和卢比奥一起参加 2028 年大选</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/03/us/politics/trump-vance-rubio-2028-election.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统表示，副总统万斯和国务卿马可·卢比奥应该平分一张票，但没有提及谁应该担任最高职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/03/us/politics/trump-vance-rubio-2028-election.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 14:53:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院将就特朗普继续伊朗战争的权力进行投票，已经来不及拖延了</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/03/us/politics/house-vote-trump-iran-war-powers.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项指示总统停止美国参与伊朗事务的措施原本有望在五月底获得通过，但共和党领导人推迟了行动。他们已经没有时间推迟投票了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/03/us/politics/house-vote-trump-iran-war-powers.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 14:17:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
