      <title>特朗普瞄准 59 个国家和欧盟征收新关税</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/03/business/trump-tariffs-force-labor.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府官员表示，他们计划对未能打击强迫劳动制造的商品的国家征收高达 12.5% 的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/03/business/trump-tariffs-force-labor.html</guid>
