    <item>
      <title>布兰奇称司法部不会继续处理特朗普的 18 亿美元基金</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/02/us/politics/todd-blanche-house-hearing.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代理总检察长告诉立法者，他将保留一项命令，迫使国税局采取行动。放弃对特朗普总统、他的家人和他的企业的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/02/us/politics/todd-blanche-house-hearing.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 02:33:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保护特朗普家族免受国税局侵害的命令布兰奇表示，审计将继续存在</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/02/us/politics/trump-irs-settlement.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代理总检察长表示，尽管放弃了 18 亿美元的支付基金，但政府仍在保留一项广泛的命令，保护总统及其家人免受对已提交申报表的审计。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/02/us/politics/trump-irs-settlement.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 00:53:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
